uation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">user-select: none</code> specifies that the text cannot be selected.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<p><span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ Requires prefixes for full support.</span>\n<br>\n<span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ This is not a secure method to prevent users from copying content.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=user-select-none\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=user-select-none</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Disable selection","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/disable-selection/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/display-table-centering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Display table centering"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/custom-variables/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Custom variables"}}}}}